author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
The video for "Rock And Roll Party Cowboy" by my own music band, The Darkness, was released yesterday and I was surprised at some of the reactions it provoked. I thought I'd share some of the comments and ask you what you think? 

You can find the video in its entirety here: https://youtu.be/UHGBsvrRQ58?si=lLcf74RkUgjojDmg

It's also the opening track from the new Darkness album "Dreams On Toast" which can be found here:  https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

For Behind The Scenes footage and JHRA related news, visit my Patreon: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

Get a Justin Hawkins Rides Again T-Shirt & Hoodie here: https://thejawsofvictory

title: An AI video? What Was I Thinking?
